      • addTransientConfigurationElement

        public void addTransientConfigurationElement(IConfigurationElement el)
        Adds a transient (ie non persistent) configuration element field to the field list. This is mainly used to add a typed field to the metadata after the system has been loaded.

        Any calls to reload() will not load these fields.

        Parameters:
        el -
